Chain casting earth pet (generally 2 pets are enough) works rather well.<br>
you can afk safely on the ledge of hill at north part.<br>
loot : you can sell all weapons/armors to the merchands into the huts, they are not on same faction ; the one in a hut at left side (when you follow path) accepts to buy, even if you are full KOS to city merchands as I am.<br>
<br>
just don't forget to get Jboots or Sow, those damn little dwarves hit with big strengh and will splash you if they can get you.<br>
